NAME
    Devel::Trepan variable watch plugin for via Variable::Magic 

SUMMARY
    This adds a "watchvar" command to the Devel::Trepan debugger.

    This plugin uses Variable::Magic to do the heavy lifting.

    See "help" inside the debugger or a list of options.

